The President is praising the creation of 10 million jobs in the past 54 months, the longest stretch of private sector job growth in history. He is urging Congress to lower the corporate tax rate, close loopholes, and simplify the tax code. The Treasury Department is taking steps to discourage companies from using corporate inversions to avoid paying taxes. The President believes in rewarding hard work, promoting fairness in the tax code, and creating more job opportunities for Americans.